Cheers.'' Like when you go on a diet and you dream of pizza. I always think of those wonderful years. I loved working on it.', 73890, 0), (467212, 'The 3-hour Diet is absolutely safe - in fact it''s not a diet, it''s a lifestyle! Once you reach your goal weight, you just adjust the portion sizes slightly to maintain that optimal weight.', 53974, 0), (467213, 'Diseases happen in acidic environments, so it''s very important to keep your body alkaline. Keeping a diet high in leafy greens, spring water, fresh air, raw almonds, lemons, grapefruits, and warm water with juice from half a lemon helps lower acidity levels.', 71995, 0), (467214, 'I actually went on a vegan diet. So I was nagging myself there. I don''t nag other people about it. It was sort of an interesting experiment, and I found it wasn''t that hard at all.', 23002, 0), (467215, 'I have been following a vegan diet now since the 1980s, and find it not only healthier, but also much more attractive than the chunks of meat that were on my plate as a child.', 72741, 0), (467216, 'A vegan diet takes care of most of what we need to do. But you''ll also want to minimize the use of oils generally, because while olive oil and other vegetable oils are better for your heart than chicken fat, they are as fattening as animal fats.', 72741, 0), (467217, 'I''m not completely vegan - my diet''s probably about 80 percent plant based, but I do eat some meat. I try to know where everything comes from, though. And all bets are off if my husband and I go to a really great restaurant.', 73891, 0), (467218, 'If you''re an actress, you''re always on one diet or another - it''s a way of life.', 70408, 0), (467219, 'My Ph.D. thesis problem was to determine if the DNA content of rat tissues increased if there was B12 in the diet. This problem was suggested by my adviser based on the observation that thymine could replace vitamin B12 in a lactobacillus.', 73892, 0), (467220, 'It''s never fun having to bulk up for a job on an action film, then lose weight for another role. I don''t actually mind working out, but it''s the diet: I''m half-French, so I love my food, and boiled chicken breast for breakfast is not my idea of a good meal.', 73893, 0), (467221, 'Leave the table while you still feel you could eat a little more.', 18698, 0), (467222, 'Everyone''s been on a ramen noodle diet once or twice.', 73894, 0), (467223, 'The sad thing is, when it comes to diet, is that even when well-intentioned Feds try to do right by us, they fail. Either they''re outvoted by puppets of agribusiness, or they are puppets of agribusiness.', 37387, 0), (467224, 'Let me pose you a question. Can farm-raised salmon be organic when its feed has nothing to do with its natural diet, even if the feed itself is supposedly organic, and the fish themselves are packed tightly in pens, swimming in their own filth?', 37387, 0), (467225, 'The USDA is not our ally here. We have to take matters into our own hands, not only by advocating for a better diet for everyone - and that''s the hard part - but by improving our own. And that happens to be quite easy. Less meat, less junk, more plants.', 37387, 0), (467226, 'I was diagnosed with a lung disorder that some people walk around with and don''t even know they have. Through early diagnosis, I''m happy to share that I stay healthy with diet and exercise.', 73895, 0), (467227, 'The vegan diet is obviously lacking whatever essential nutrient it is that makes people likeable.', 15803, 0), (467228, 'Like everyone, there are times when I just don''t feel like exercising. When that happens, I''m a bit more careful with my diet. But on days I really want a treat, like chocolate, I work out a little harder. I don''t believe in beating myself up for not being ''good.''', 73896, 0), (467229, 'If you''re feeling frumpy or grumpy, try to eat Paleo. It''s a way of eating that is sometimes referred to as the ''Caveman Diet.''', 73897, 0), (467230, 'I really don''t follow a strict diet I just watch 